data.description: Fantastic home just outside of town! Here's a great opportunity to buy an awesome home on 5 acres just minutes from town. This beautiful split foyer home has been extensively updated with all new flooring, paint, light fixtures and bathrooms. It also has a new roof, hvac and hot water heater. You can tell by the details that a lot of work went into the tasteful choices that the seller has made while updating this home. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 1 bath on the main level with 2 extra large rooms and a  second full bath downstairs that could be used as additional bedrooms or for whatever the new owner decides. Outside the views are stunning. Around back there's a nice deck and patio area with a beautiful pool to enjoy the warm summer days.  Located in a great area and sits far enough of the road to allow for plenty of privacy.
